<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
	<title>Circle</title>
	<link href="css/wap.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="bgfff">
	<!--内容-->
	<section class="content">
		<article class="directions-page">
			<div class="item info-item">
				<p>CC币是Circle系统虚拟货币，可以在Circle内置换大礼（即将上线，敬请期待）、解锁表情包等。</p>
			</div>
			<div class="item">
				<p>当前版本Circle如何获得CC币:</p>
				<p>1.用户粉丝增长获得CC币</p>
				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="item-table table-row-2">
					<tr>
						<th>获得第x个粉丝</th>
						<th>奖励cc币</th>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>1</td>
						<td>1</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>50</td>
						<td>20</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>200</td>
						<td>50</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>500</td>
						<td>100</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>1000</td>
						<td>150</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>5000</td>
						<td>200</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>10000</td>
						<td>200</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>15000</td>
						<td>200</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>20000</td>
						<td>200</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>每增加5000</td>
						<td>200</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</div>
			<div class="item">
				<p>2.作为圈主,圈子内粉丝增长获得CC币</p>
				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="item-table table-row-2">
					<tr>
						<th>获得第x个成员</th>
						<th>奖励cc币</th>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>50</td>
						<td>10</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>200</td>
						<td>10</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>500</td>
						<td>10</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>1000</td>
						<td>10</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>5000</td>
						<td>10</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>10000</td>
