						<td>每增加5000</td>
						<td>10</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</div>
			<div class="item">
				<p>3.用户秀获赞从而获得CC币</p>
				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="item-table table-row-2">
					<tr>
						<th>获得第x个赞</th>
						<th>奖励cc币</th>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>1</td>
